      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h2><span class="section-num">1.</span>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      Fourth-generation cranberry farmer and systems builder working at the intersection 
      of agricultural tradition and modern technology. My work focuses on building 
      infrastructure—physical and digital—that creates lasting capability.
    </p>

    <h2><span class="section-num">2.</span>Background</h2>
    <div class="bio-grid">
      <div class="bio-section">
        <h3>Positions</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>General Manager, Elm Lake Cranberry</li>
          <li>Founder, Elm Lake Labs</li>
          <li>President, Wisconsin Cranberry Board</li>
          <li>Ocean Spray Grower</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bio-section">
        <h3>Focus Areas</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Agricultural Operations</li>
          <li>Precision Agriculture</li>
          <li>Systems Design</li>
          <li>Infrastructure Development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="section-num">3.</span>Current Projects</h2>

    <div class="project-entry">
      <div class="project-title">Elm Lake Cranberry</div>
      <div class="project-desc">
        150-acre cranberry operation integrating automated irrigation, environmental sensors, 
        and precision agriculture technologies.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-entry">
      <div class="project-title">Elm Lake Labs</div>
      <div class="project-desc">
        Agricultural technology consultancy and FJ Dynamics dealership serving regional growers.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-entry">
      <div class="project-title">Blossom</div>
      <div class="project-desc">
        Software-as-a-service platform for comprehensive farm management and operations tracking.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-entry">
      <div class="project-title">Pinpoint</div>
      <div class="project-desc">
        Mobile application for field scouting, pest identification, and agronomic data collection.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-entry">
      <div class="project-title">CranBase</div>
      <div class="project-desc">
        AI-powered database synthesizing cranberry research literature and production insights.
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2><span class="section-num">4.</span>Philosophy</h2>
    <p>
      Building systems that reduce friction, create leverage, and leave people more capable 
      than before. Whether managing water flow across 150 acres or information flow across 
      an industry, the underlying principles remain consistent.
    </p>
  </main>

